About us
The Axe Trap is committed to providing the best axe throwing experience for all size groups. Whether you want to throw alone, with a friend or the whole family, we will ensure you have a good time. We can accommodate private parties as well as team-building and corporate events. We also host the
WATL National League
as well as local leagues. Our team of AXEperts are here to keep our guests safe and
create an unforgettable experience.
Our venue is the modern version of a 1920's industrial warehouse with open ceiling trusses that are 20 feet high and span over 5,000 square feet of interior space. We have a 1,200 square foot outdoor deck that can be enjoyed as part of the whole venue or rented separately.The Axe Trap and The Trap were founded by Manny Perez and David Varnagy, local vascular surgeons, entrepreneurs, and philanthropists with the vision to provide a modern industrial community gathering place for all to enjoy.

Events
BARBARELLA NIGHT
Saturday September 13th
Sunday may 8th
Barbarella Orlando is now hosting their 80's new wave nights at The Trap every Saturday from 9:30pm - 2am.  Every 3rd Saturday is Memento Mori with dark wave! $10 cover
09:30 PM - 02:00 AM
SALSA SUNDAY
Sunday September 14th
Sunday may 8th
Join us and MamboYa Dance Company for Salsa Sundays at The Trap! Dance lessons, social dancing, performances and a live DJ mixing the best of salsa, bachata and cha cha cha keeps it lively from 5pm - 10pm. $20 Admission. Ask about the military and college student discount!
05:00 PM - 10:00 PM
TRIVIA NIGHT
Wednesday September 17th
Sunday may 8th
Join us for Trivia Night every Wednesday at 7pm with Curtis Earth Trivia! Did you know Curtis Earth was voted BEST trivia host five times by Orlando Weekly? Play for free and play for the chance to win gift card prizes while enjoying our Wednesday Trivia special: $10 flatbreads and cocktails!
07:00 PM - 08:00 PM
RAGNAROCKING THE TRAP
Thursday October 9th
Sunday may 8th
Join us on October 9th for a family friendly Viking themed event at The Trap! $5 entry fee to participate in the costume contest, $15 axe throwing special and trunk or treat event! Enjoy $10 viking themed cocktails crafted specifically for this action packed event!
06:00 PM - 08:00 PM
